&\phantom{=}+
\left\{\mbox{各期の変数}2\mbox{の誤差}(w_{1}, w_{2}, \dots, w_{J})\right\}^{2}\mbox{の和}\\
&\phantom{=}\dots
+\left\{\mbox{各期の変数}I+1\mbox{の誤差}(w_{1}, w_{2}, \dots, w_{J})\right\}^{2}\mbox{の和}
